parameters:
Dining Hall Chef: There's an ingredient that I can't handle.
Can you help me?

Dining Hall Chef: Alright, I understand. I'll ask someone
else.

Dining Hall Chef: I've been waiting for those words! Let's
go to the kitchen!

Dining Hall Chef: Thank you so much! This is my gratitude
for helping me!
実績 お料理の達人
Dining Hall Chef: A-Are you okay...? You're not dead, right?

Traveling Goods Merchant: 'Lately, there have been a lot of
bandits on the road. It's profitable for adventurers like
Mucos, but it's also dangerous.'

Gourmet Koriba: When you become famous, you can't even
relax. Today is a completely private day, so please be
quiet.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Gourmet Coriba: Do you have any business with me? Is there a
need to interrupt me while I'm savoring wine?

Clea: I'll get straight to the point. Could you step down as
a judge for the cooking competition?

Gourmet Coriba: So you're the negotiators from the Tokyo
side, huh? What do you bring to me then?

Gourmet Coriba: Baer left an outrageous amount of money!
It's nothing but pocket change when I become a court chef.

Thief Nora: D-Determining victory or defeat with money...
that's absurd!

Gourmet Coriba: It's only natural that the strongest one
wins, and being a court chef is part of the political world.

Gourmet Coriba: It's impossible for someone who has only
gained popularity to come this far in Tokyo. Above all,
because of my chronic illness, I can't cook properly, right?

Gourmet Coriba: There is no representative with skills as
great as that man. This match was already over when Baer
initiated the challenge.
Thief Nora: At the very least, let us have a fair match!
Thief Nora: With this, the owner will be pitiful...

Gourmet Coriba: Hahaha, if Tokyo loses, the prestigious
reputation of Restaurant La Miro will also be tarnished.

Gourmet Coriba: Let's talk in the room I'm borrowing. I'll
tell you something I love as much as gourmet food.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Gourmet Koriba: P-Please, forgive me! I'll do this, so
please don't get involved with me!

Gourmet Koriba: For the time being, I don't want to get
involved with anyone... especially women.

Gourmet Koriba: I... I don't want to get involved with you
guys...

parameters:
Male Deliveryman: It's better not to go to the Mucos Old
Road. It seems to have become the stronghold of the escaped
bandits.

Innkeeper: The person at the leftmost seat seems to be
someone famous, but I've never heard of them...

Innkeeper: We have food and lodging available. Please come
and rest your weary traveler's soul.
